social_posts.post_text:
Presenting a new sculptural work by @casey__mccafferty: A table carved by hand from ash with dark-green hued soapstone, and the artists signature juxtaposing textures.⁠
⁠
View now at @fogfair - come and find us at booth 111.⁠
⁠
Gallery FUMI at FOG Design+Art | Booth 111, 18 - 21 January, Fort Mason Center, San Francisco⁠
